m.com/p/awx4n2zg/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/11/5f32b660cf7177791.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><span class="embed-card  main-site res_smzdm" style=""><a target="_blank" onclick="dataLayer.push({'event':'1200041','pagetitle':'努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜'});" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://wiki.smzdm.com/" ><span class="z-tag-baike res_smzdm">百科</span></a><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="dataLayer.push({'event':'1200041','pagetitle':'努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜'});" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://wiki.smzdm.com/p/ej0nm11/" ><img ol  alt="努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜" class="res_smzdm" src="https://y.zdmimg.com/202007/05/5f01603a7ad0a2745.jpg_a200.jpg" ></a></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="dataLayer.push({'event':'1200041','pagetitle':'努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜'});" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://wiki.smzdm.com/p/ej0nm11/" ><span class="card-name res_smzdm">元気森林 苏打气泡水</span></a><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <i>值</i>0</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <i>点评</i>0</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <i>原创</i>0</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <i>好价</i>0</span><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'元気森林 苏打气泡水','id':'awx4n2zg' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'67.9','brand':'无' ,'mall':'无', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'67.9','dimension10':'smzdm.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'3阶价格','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/ec95f231b5f858a3/ca_bb_yc_95_71010698_12540_2559_111_0"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></a><a target="_blank" onclick="dataLayer.push({'event':'1200041','pagetitle':'努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜'});" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://wiki.smzdm.com/p/ej0nm11/" ><span class="card-btn-light res_smzdm">看百科</span></a><span style="color:red">¥67.9起</span></a></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description">还有「Chang泰象苏打水」，是我冷藏室里的小秘密。深夜撬开瓶盖，假装自己在喝酒。做柠檬苏打水它也是最佳拍档，加切片的柠檬和嫩仔姜，更有层次丰富的快乐。 </p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx4n2zg/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/11/5f32b694515d38169.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a> </p><h2 id="cl_2">× 奶茶</h2><p itemprop="description">虽然元气森林的气泡水堪称业界翘楚，但奶茶是真的不~好~喝~啊~</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx4n2zg/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/11/5f32b6b7a528c4560.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">刚喝第一瓶的时候蛮惊艳的，达到了瓶装奶茶的及格水平，非常接近阿萨姆奶茶的味道。但越喝越是喝不下去，甜甜腻腻的味道好像飘在空中，一点不真实。（好评那么多，认为不好喝的时候心里都在质问自己：你是不是没品味！）</p><p itemprop="description">唯一的优点大概就是无糖、低卡，相对健康吧。实在想喝奶茶的话，还是老老实实动手煮茶冲奶，或者等血糖低下来再去奶茶店好了T^T</p><h2 id="cl_3">√ 甜和不甜的无糖酸奶</h2><p itemprop="description"> 有些酸奶，虽然没添加蔗糖，但因为加入了代糖，所以口味依然可以酸酸甜甜。</p><p itemprop="description">「<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/20983/" data-brandid="20983" target="_blank">君乐宝</a>简醇」是其中最喜欢的，常温下可保存，加上拧盖的瓶装设计，方便出门携带。口感十分浓厚，可以直观理解为无蔗糖版的安慕希。 </p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx4n2zg/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/11/5f32b6d66d7875067.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">如果能接受原味酸奶的酸度，那么完全不甜的无糖酸奶里，出色的选择更多。</p><p itemprop="description">「乐纯三三三倍希腊式发酵乳」是口感最扎实的无糖酸奶之一，不额外添加蔗糖，低脂肪高蛋白质，美味度完全满足“舔盖党”的高要求。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/awx4n2zg/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="努力寻找每一点甜蜜：我的无糖零食红黑榜" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/11/5f32b7069939d7373.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><span class="embed-card  main-site res_smzdm" style=""><a target="_blank" onclick="