><strong><span style="font-size:10.5pt;">面料透气性</span></strong><span style="font-size:10.5pt;">：透气性一般，面料摸起来还是很厚的，运动过程中的舒适度也一般。</span></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>衣服做工：</strong></p><p itemprop="description">最特别的是领口的标签是塑料的，方便撕下来；</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar0vxvv7/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="小米有品热销前5不超50块的运动T恤值不值得买？" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/07/5f2d4bd3af1127039.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">袖口的水洗麦就有点多余；</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar0vxvv7/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="小米有品热销前5不超50块的运动T恤值不值得买？" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/07/5f2d4bd41a5089579.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">袖子处采用了平缝的工艺，其它地方也是传统的缝合工艺；</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar0vxvv7/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="小米有品热销前5不超50块的运动T恤值不值得买？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/07/5f2d4bd4707ec8323.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;;font-size:10.5pt;"></span></p><p itemprop="description"> <strong>三、<span style="font-size:10.5pt;">早风</span></strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar0vxvv7/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="小米有品热销前5不超50块的运动T恤值不值得买？" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/07/5f2d4c9da51d19803.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><strong>价格：35</strong></p>
