ension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://shop.revolution.watch/divers-sixty-five-honey-for-the-rake-and-revolution-4.html"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">shop.revolution.watch</span></a><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'65 honey','id':'aekwml3m' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'无', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'watch','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://shop.revolution.watch/divers-sixty-five-honey-for-the-rake-and-revolution-4.html"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></a></span></span></span></dir><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><p itemprop="description"> <br/></p><h3>3. 豪利时潜水海洋清洁第三代特别版</h3><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekwml3m/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="豪利时，说爱的确不容易" title="" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/11/5f326a3298d0e934.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aekwml3m/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="豪利时，说爱的确不容易" title="" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/11/5f326a32a7cdf8857.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">潜水系列实际上是豪利时的老系列了，采用的也是中规中矩的潜水表配置，防水300米、陶瓷圈等，比较特别的是表盘的放射拉丝工艺很到位，而且背后的海洋回收塑料也是个亮点，创意还是很足的。近年豪利时不知道是不是突然从沛纳海身上找到了灵感，各种大规模限量层出不穷，都是在常规款上做改动，比如贝加尔湖限量还有早前的星球大战限量，噱头够了，可在能否吸引消费者掏钱这一方面是不是够，那就见仁见智了。就像前两年发布的限量版星球大战，某些钟表网站都快吹上天了，结果过去一年多了，还没卖完.... 更需要谨慎购买的是某些国内无良钟表媒体恰烂饭，65绿色表盘上打个logo就敢出来卖，一个个大佬出来站台劝韭菜买，我觉得这简直太low了。</p>
