</span></div><p itemprop="description"> <a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/46558/" data-brandid="46558" target="_blank">乐乐趣</a>的立体情绪绘本。</p><p itemprop="description">这本书最特别的地方是把5类常见的情绪和色彩对标。</p><p itemprop="description">伤心难过是像下雨一样的蓝色。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aoozpq57/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img alt="800家幼儿园园长推荐，入选小学课程读本，影响3-10岁孩子一生的好书" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202008/10/5f30fee54ab1a8209.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">开心像明亮的黄色。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aoozpq57/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="800家幼儿园园长推荐，入选小学课程读本，影响3-10岁孩子一生的好书" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202008/10/5f3103c4596753791.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">这套书的立体机关做得也很有趣。<br/></p><p itemprop="description">绿色是平静。</p><p itemprop="description">打开躺在一张吊床上。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aoozpq57/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="800家幼儿园园长推荐，入选小学课程读本，影响3-10岁孩子一生的好书" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202008/10/5f30fee55121c5844.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">红色是生气，打开就会张牙舞爪。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aoozpq57/pic_17/' target='_blank'><img alt="800家幼儿园园长推荐，入选小学课程读本，影响3-10岁孩子一生的好书" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202008/10/5f30fee54ee289966.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 150, 0);"><strong>查理和劳拉</strong></span></p><p itemprop="description" style="text-align: center;"><strong>（英）罗伦.乔尔德</strong></p><p itemprop="description" style="text-align: center;"><strong>推荐年龄：3-6岁</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aoozpq57/pic_18/' target='_blank'><img alt="800家幼儿园园长推荐，入选小学课程读本，影响3-10岁孩子一生的好书" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202008/10/5f30fee5819504627.jpg_e680.jpg" title=""/></a></p>
